1 Total $5,000,000
21 Agricultural Marketing Loan Fund
3 Provides funds to support the activities of the fund.
4 Total $5,000,000
54 DEPARTMENT OF ADMINISTRATIVE AND FINANCIAL SERVICES
6 Dirigo Business Incentives Program
7 Provides funds for agriculturally directed spending.
8 Total $10,000,000
98 Agricultural Buildings Property Tax Exemption Program
10 Provides funds to exempt certain agricultural buildings from property taxation for a 10-
11 year period.
